<div class="center"><br />Turns out Dave was at Murphy's for lunch, then returned to work with grave consequences</div>
<p>Despite the winds and the fact that it's November, Frenzy numbers were strong today. We had four and a half warm bodies&mdash;Dave and I count as 0.75ea, if you're wondering!</p>
<p>Though we were ambitious in planning for Super-Flag, I think everyone was content to settle for the traffic-less ramps of the Amphitheater Road. I know I was anyhow.</p>
